FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784735286
OL,3,CCouple found dead at cider festival
OL,4,Cdied from carbon monoxide poisoning
OL,6,FTheir inquests held separately at
OL,7,FWinchester Coroner's Court on
OL,8,FWednesday heard the business owner and
OL,9,Ftrainee accountant had gone to the
OL,10,Ffair to sell crafts and stayed in
OL,11,Ftheir van in a field for exhibitors on
OL,12,Fsite.
OL,14,FThey were discovered dead by fellow
OL,15,Fexhibitor Alexander Huxley, who had
OL,16,Fmet the pair the night before over
OL,17,Fdrinks and music, after he thought it
OL,18,Fwas strange they did not turn up to
OL,19,Ftheir stall at around 11.30 the next
OL,20,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784735286
OL,3,CCouple found dead at cider festival
OL,4,Cdied from carbon monoxide poisoning
OL,6,FHe went to check on them and when he
OL,7,Fopened the door was met with a strong
OL,8,Fsmell of gas, the inquest heard.
OL,10,FHe found a gas heater with a canister
OL,11,Fattached to it, and saw the couple not
OL,12,Fmoving in the back of the van and
OL,13,F"turned around in shock".
OL,15,FAn inspection of the gas heater and
OL,16,Fcylinder after the couple's deaths
OL,17,Ffound it had been used with 10% of gas
OL,18,Fleft in the cylinder, and the heater
OL,19,Fwas not securely fitted to the gas
OL,20,Fbottle and a gas leak was found.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
