OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784735286
OL,3,CCouple found dead at cider festival
OL,4,Cdied from carbon monoxide poisoning
OL,6,FHampshire area coroner Rosamund Rhodes-
OL,7,FKemp said: "We'll never know how the
OL,8,Fconnection became disconnected."
OL,10,FGiving evidence at the inquest, Howard
OL,11,FJonas for Flogas, the company that
OL,12,Fcarried out the inspection, added that
OL,13,Fparabolic heaters should only be used
OL,14,Foutdoors or in well ventilated spaces.
OL,16,FIn the facts of the case, the coroner
OL,17,Fsaid: "Overnight on the 11th they
OL,18,Fsuffered carbon monoxide poisoning due
OL,19,Fto running a camper gas cylinder with
OL,20,Fa heater that was not designed for use
OL,21,Fin an inside environment."
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@`O]yD@GOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784735286
OL,3,CCouple found dead at cider festival
OL,4,Cdied from carbon monoxide poisoning
OL,6,FShe told the families she could not
OL,7,Fconclude their deaths were accidental
OL,8,Fbecause it was a deliberate act to put
OL,9,Fthe heating on "with a totally
OL,10,Funintended consequence".
OL,12,FInstead she concluded their deaths
OL,13,Fwere misadventure.
OL,15,FThe coroner however raised concerns
OL,16,Fover whether a safety warning is
OL,17,Fpresent on heaters to say they cannot
OL,18,Fbe used in enclosed spaces.
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784735286
OL,3,CCouple found dead at cider festival
OL,4,Cdied from carbon monoxide poisoning
OL,6,FMs Rhodes-Kemp said: "I will be
OL,7,Fcontacting the manufacturers of the
OL,8,Fheater to see whether a warning is on
OL,9,Fthe device itself, I think that may
OL,10,Fprevent a future death.
OL,12,F"All I can say is I am terribly sorry
OL,13,Fbecause it's an absolute tragedy for
OL,14,Ftwo young people to die like this."
OL,16,FThe coroner added the butane gas smell
OL,17,Fdetected by Mr Huxley was largely
OL,18,Firrelevant to their deaths as it was
OL,19,Fnon-smelling carbon monoxide toxicity
OL,20,Fthat was the cause of death.
OL,26,@nD@VOUtD@AOUvD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
