OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784735286
OL,3,CCouple found dead at cider festival
OL,4,Cdied from carbon monoxide poisoning
OL,6,FFamily members who attended the
OL,7,Fhearings described Kayleigh Coll as
OL,8,Fthe most kind person you could ever
OL,9,Fmeet, and Christopher Coll as a very
OL,10,Floving, good person who "absolutely
OL,11,Fadored" his children and had goals to
OL,12,Flive off the land and be self-
OL,13,Fsufficient.
OL,15,FThe inquest for Ms Coll heard from her
OL,16,Ffamily that this was a one occasion
OL,17,Fthe couple slept in the van, as a "one
OL,18,Foff" as they tried to get their
OL,19,Fbusiness off the ground.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@GO]yD@cOUzD@DO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
